name: Neura v001
description: A portrait of a woman, re-imagined by a deep neural network. This portrait has been drawn by a deep learning algorithm, using a technique called “style transfer”. The size has been capped at 1280x1280 px to speed up the processing. Original image source: https://unsplash.com/photos/xOjzehJ49Hk Thanks  to https://unsplash.com/@omidarmin for the amazing photo.
